snippet.title: Typeds Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The space war started here and now! The victory depends only on you and all your years as a gamer. Show what you are capable of and destroy everything by writing quickly and correctly! "The keyboard is your weapon!"

The launch of Typeds comes with a small discount, so add it to your wishlist to stay up to date
